snippet.title: Aether Singularity teaser 1
snippet.description:
Here's a look at our first game, Aether Singularity!
With gameplay inspired by Parasite Eve, take on the role of a special government agent as you fight against invading demons!

Do you have what it takes?


Twitter: https://twitter.com/AlenarSoft
Itch.io: https://alenar-soft.itch.io/
